   Familiar accusations, often trotted out, and surely no murdering
matter. There is more to it.
</P>
<P>
   America's vulnerability is an adjunct of its peculiar strength.
As sole surviving superpower, without benefit of false modesty, it
stands out distinctly from the crowd, a potential target for
snipers.
</P>
