   OBIT-PALM _ Michael Palm, 47, innovator in method of
reinsurance.
</P>
<P>
   OBIT-STOKES _ Isaac Stokes, 91, lawyer during new deal and at
U.N. birth.
</P>
<P>
   OBIT-BILBY _ Richard Mansfield Bilby, 67, judge in Charles
