   BOOKS-KAHN _ AUSTIN, Texas _ When Sharon Kahn started writing
fiction again, it was with a sense of urgency. She just turned 64.
What separates her from other Austin grandmothers typing novels in
their living rooms is that Simon &AMP; Schuster just published her
book. (Morris, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED.
</P>
