   DAVE-MATTHEWS _ An unlikely rock star if ever there was one,
Dave Matthews has nonetheless stumbled dumbfounded into the ranks
of '90s pop-culture sensations. (Riemenschneider, Austin
American-Statesman) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-AVENGERS _ A tragically miscast Uma Thurman flounders.
