Corp.-NationsBank Corp. merger could cover the $10 monthly checking
charge for 2.3 million account holders for a year. ... Or pay the
$25 annual fee for 920,000 credit card customers. ... Or pay the
yearly salaries of about 80 tellers. By VICTORIA COLLIVER.
