<DOCNO> NYT19980814.0130 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-14 13:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4116 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ANIMAL-RIGHTS-HNS &LR;      08-14 0518
</HEADER>
