   SUNDAY FINANCIAL
</P>
<P>
   Here is a preliminary look at the graphics scheduled for the
Sunday financial section of The Times. These graphics will be
transmitted Friday evening. The descriptions and sizes are
tentative. Please check tomorrow's late budget for stories and
specific graphics.
</P>
<P>
   MARKET/Historic Valuations -- Size tk --
(BC-MARKET-OVERVIEW-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   S&AMP;P chart showing where stocks should be at different historic
valuations
</P>
<P>
   MUTFUND/Summer Buys -- 2 x 3 1/4 -- (BC-MUTFUND-BUYS-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   What three money managers buy on the summer sell-off
</P>
<P>
   INVEST/Defensive Strategies -- 2 x 3 1/4 --
