<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-14 14:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4302 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-IT-MATTERS-DAMMIT!-RE     08-14 1319
