HOT-TIPS (Los Angeles) _ It's no big surprise that Harrison Ford
was voted the sexiest man alive...or that ``Ally McBeal'' was rated
the sexiest TV show in a national poll of women readers for InStyle
magazine. But perfume manufacturers might get their noses out of
joint learning that the sexiest scent in America is ... soap. By
Barbara De Witt. 
