   Great Northern Press of Wilkes-Barre won a $137,024 contract
from the Government Printing Office in Washington, D.C., for
printing services.
</P>
<P>
   Five Thirty Corp. of Fort Washington won a $1.5 million contract
from the Fleet and Industrial Supply Center in Philadelphia for
transportation services.
</P>
<P>
   Boeing Helicopters of Ridley Park won a $262,763 contract from
the Defense Supply Center in Columbus, Ohio, for aircraft
components.
</P>
<P>
   Boeing Helicopters of Ridley Park won a $405,966 contract from
the Defense Supply Center in Columbus, Ohio, for mechanical power
transmission equipment.
