BURIALS (Washington) - For the second time in a month, House
Veterans Affairs Committee Chairman and Arizonan Bob Stump is
protesting the burial of American heroes in Arlington National
Cemetery. The Clinton Administration requested waivers of the
veterans' service requirement for burial in the nations most
