<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-WOMEN-POLICE-MEET-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDITORS:
</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles-datelined WOMEN-POLICE-MEET will not move in
tonight's Los Angeles Daily News file. 

